      • checkHealingItemTime

        public double checkHealingItemTime(double currentTime)
        Check whether the apply time on a HealingItem has been fulfilled. After certain time applies a percentage of the health benefit and reduces the amount remaining
        Parameters:
        currentTime - a double the time in seconds since the start of play
        Returns:
        a double the time remaining before the HealingItem will fully apply. O if it can apply now, or if none present.
